A [[en/Community/Patches/Patches]] that allows you to change how long error messages are displayed for before automatically closing.

== Description ==
This patch allows you to change the duration for which [[en/Error messages]] are displayed before automatically closing.

== Use ==
This feature is set to 5 seconds by default. Modify the duration through the [[en/Archive/Manual/Settings/Configuring patches/Construction|configure patches -> construction]] window or use the following syntax in [[en/Archive/Manual/Settings/Openttd.cfg]]:
<pre>[patches]
errmsg_duration = (number of seconds)</pre>

